  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to identify molecular features predicting response or resistance to
      cetuximab
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Secondary objective is to investigate association of genomic status of EGFR and HER-2 genes
      with clinical outcome, including objective response, time to progression and survival
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
